ewline &amp;	exttt{\qquad int age}
ewline &amp;	ext{}
ewline &amp;	exttt{\qquad void noise():}
ewline &amp;	exttt{\qquad\qquad print(&ldquo;pet noises&rdquo;)} \end{align*} $$
Could we do the same thing?
